PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,FThe PSNI said it had launched an
OL,7,Foperation relating to dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving from Saturday morning with a
OL,9,F"large number of young people seen
OL,10,Ftravelling at speed and dangerously on
OL,11,Fscrambler-type bikes".
OL,13,FIt said riders had their faces
OL,14,Fpartially covered, were not wearing
OL,15,Fhelmets and driving "without care for
OL,16,Ftheir safety or those around them".
OL,18,FIt said evidence gathering is taking
OL,19,Fplace to identify those responsible.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@UO]wD@UOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
