FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,FBins and loading cages were placed
OL,7,Facross part of the Stewartstown Road
OL,8,Fat its junction with Bell Steel Road,
OL,9,Fwith fires being set from some of
OL,10,Fthose bins.
OL,12,FThe road was closed for a time and the
OL,13,Fpublic was advised to avoid the area.
OL,15,FThe PSNI said large crowds of up to
OL,16,F100 people gathered, many aged in
OL,17,Ftheir early teens, throwing masonry at
OL,18,Fpolice with 11 police vehicles damaged
OL,19,F` 10 Land Rovers and one car ` on
OL,20,FSaturday evening and one officer was
OL,21,Fassaulted.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
