PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,FOne male was arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fdisorderly behaviour and a man aged 27
OL,8,Fwas arrested for disorderly behaviour
OL,9,Fand common law riot.
OL,11,FA serious assault involving iron bars
OL,12,Fresulted in a man being taken to
OL,13,Fhospital, with a man in his 20s
OL,14,Farrested on suspicion of assault and
OL,15,Fdisorderly behaviour.
OL,17,FPolice used stingers on a number of
OL,18,Fvehicles and a scrambler was seized.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
