PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,FIts 17-year-old rider was interviewed
OL,7,Ffor dangerous driving, no licence, no
OL,8,Finsurance and no number plate ` with a
OL,9,Freport to be submitted to the Public
OL,10,FProsecution Service.
OL,12,FSpeaking to UTV Sinn Fein MLA Danny
OL,13,FBaker said: "Like many communities we
OL,14,Fare facing an increase of e-scooters
OL,15,Fand motorbikes but in recent weeks
OL,16,Fthat has really escalated.
OL,26,@tD@Wrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
