OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,F"Last night we had terrible behaviour.
OL,7,FWe had 100's of people down to watch
OL,8,Fmotorbikes take over the roads and
OL,9,Ffrom that massive disorder police came
OL,10,Funder attack.
OL,12,F"We'll keep working with youth workers
OL,13,Fand buisnesses and find solutions
OL,14,Ftogether."
OL,16,FChief Inspector Kelly Gibson, West
OL,17,FBelfast Area Commander, said: "We know
OL,18,Fthe level of local concern on last
OL,19,Fnight's incident and on previous
OL,20,Fnights of dangerous and risk-taking
OL,21,Fbehaviour.
OL,26,@yD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,F"These were disgraceful scenes and we
OL,7,Fare doing all we can to keep the Colin
OL,8,Fcommunity safe.
OL,10,F"We are reviewing evidence gained from
OL,11,Flast night's disgraceful behaviour and
OL,12,Fwill be making more arrests."
OL,14,FChief Inspector Gibson added:
OL,15,F"Targeted patrols will continue in the
OL,16,FStewartstown Road and other areas to
OL,17,Fdetect offenders on bikers who are
OL,18,Fdriving illegally and dangerously."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@]O]wD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
