PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,FThe senior police officer warned those
OL,7,Finvolved they were "causing
OL,8,Fdestruction" within their own
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,F"People have a right to live in peace
OL,12,Fand to feel safe in their communities
OL,13,Fand this must stop.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@LO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
