PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1784479680
OL,3,CThree men arrested after a night of
OL,4,Cdisorder in west Belfast
OL,6,F"Parents and guardians, speak to your
OL,7,Fyoung people and warn them of the
OL,8,Fdangers of getting involved in
OL,9,Fbehaviour which could result in them
OL,10,Finjuring themselves, others, or
OL,11,Fultimately, with a criminal record
OL,12,Fwhich could have an impact on their
OL,13,Ffuture employment and even travel."
OL,15,FEarlier this week, a 31-year-old man
OL,16,Fand a 42-year-old woman were charged
OL,17,Fwith a number of offences in relation
OL,18,Fto a report of three non-legal
OL,19,Fscramblers being ridden dangerously in
OL,20,Fthe Stewartstown Road area.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
